          "reviewBody": "So sad that our school has increased so much fees but still can't provide basic amenities like hand wash and sanitizer in school. And teacher is teaching concept that everyone should wash their hands properly with handwash to be in good health. When my son asked today that there is no handwash or no soap in toilet so teacher replied him that bring your own soap or sanitizer. As there is too much crowd in recess that all kids use it so much or kids spill it on the floor to waste it. So school is not keeping it.\nAt least sanitizer is basic essential required everywhere after covid. Also school is the place from where infection spreads.",
